author: ShawnMarie
title: High playability, love the little cones
review: This set was purchased for my son who is all things trucks.  I put it together and it was a fun little build, a little more complicated than you might think.  The place where this set shines is in playability, it worked well with my son's other trucks from various types of sets and became an everyday toy for him.  I am in love with the adorable little cones.
